data.description: If you dream of quiet country living in a fabulous Barndominium set on a beautiful 14.3 acres +/- with a private drive for access. A place where you can seat yourself morning, noon, or night on the covered front porch and enjoy your morning java or crack open a cold one as you lounge by your private pool. Home features 3 bedrooms and 2.5 baths large open 1 level floor plan. Master suite is amazing with private views of the pastures that can be seen from the bedroom and dreamy master bath with 2 head shower and soaking tub. Master walk-in closet is HUGE! Stained concrete floors are perfect touch to this farm and easy to maintain. Great room features kitchen, tv area and dining room area with chandeliers. Kitchen features granite countertops and all maple cabinets with custom stain. Two bay garage area perfect for storage or converting into a man-cave or she-shed.   Pool features cabana with water and power. Heated and Cooled half bath with outdoor access for entertaining. Two fenced pastures are ready to house livestock and feature a  pond and two spigots for water. Shed 18X24(contains well house) in pasture for ease of access. 12X26 barn w/ roll up door and man door that could be easily converted to a barn. All of this a just minutes from entertainment, main interstates and more. This property will not be on the market long. It is getting to pool season so get your appointment made today. By appointment showing only agent must accompany.
